	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Akira (J) [hM04][t1].nes
<br />PRG ROM:    8 x 16KiB
<br />CHR ROM:   32 x  8KiB
<br />ROM CRC32:  0xdcb096a9
<br />ROM MD5:  0x8a04b2495442ed9a63d43c870e7cf145
<br />Mapper #:  4
<br />Mapper name: MMC3
<br />Mirroring: Horizontal
<br />Battery-backed: No
<br />Trained: Yes
<br />
<br />Only FCEUX can run it. I don't know if it has any bug.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


